Package grafo

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • grafo.Edge
  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    Class: Edge.Java An object edge is an object between two nodes of a graph. An edge has as fields the index of the node that this edge is pointing at a weight and a pherormone level. The weight represents the weight of the connection.
